          <td width="689" valign="top" background="images/bg01.jpg"> <p> 
              <B><font color='#FF3300' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='2'>Small Update<BR></B></font><font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'>2006-06-16 14:36:51&nbsp;-&nbsp;<font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'><I>Melia</I>&nbsp;              </font><br>
              <img src="images/content_bar.jpg" width="645" height="1"></p>
            <p>
<font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='2'>		
Keeping up with our trend, this update is late, but it covers most of everything!<br />
<br />
<b><u>Checklist</b></u><br />
<br />
Skeram: Check<br />
Bug Trio: Check, Check, Check<br />
Sartura: Check<br />
Fankriss: Check<br />
Huhuran: Check<br />
Twin Emperors: Check, Check<br />
Viscidus: Check<br />
Ouro: Check<br />
C'thun: Check<br />
<br />
Melia creating educational video for new apps: Check!<br />
<br />
<object width="425" height="350"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/TCp57KWUFrk"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/TCp57KWUFrk" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="425" height="350"></embed></object><br />
<br />
<br />
<b>In Other News</b>, Fires of Heaven has added a couple of new members, welcome! <br />
<br />
Due to some server drama, we had gotten a ton of applications at once; being as we are pretty much full (short of people not logging on once or twice per week), we have been trying to make room for new faces. We wanted to formally thank those who did apply to our guild and apologize to those we were not or may not be able to take in; we just simply do not have much room. It has been a lot of fun raiding with some new faces, and were happy that two of you were able to experience your first C’thun kill with us (you were so happy, half of us got happy for no reason), as well as some of our applicants being present for our first Viscidus kill. <br />
<br />
We really do wish we could keep more of you and are sorry some will be homeless; we will look you up first should we get any space. This may be the first (and possibly only) time you will see praises going out to applicants, but some of you are very dedicated and you deserve a shout-out, at the least. Hopefully, <a href="http://wow.fohguild.org/gallery/d/1464-1/shamanpenir.jpg"><font color="yellow">this</font></a> guy sends in an application when he hits level 60. He's got potential!<br />
<br />
Thank you from all of us!<br />
<br />
<b>What’s Next?</b><br />
<br />
We will continue to prepare for the next content patch and are all eagerly awaiting its chance to ram-our-asses. <br />
<br />
What do I plan to conquer first in <a href="http://wow.fohguild.org/gallery/d/1461-2/naxxramas1ir.jpg"><font color="yellow">Naxxramas?</font></a> I’m hitting up <a href="http://wow.fohguild.org/gallery/d/1462-1/mall-of_A-map.gif"><font color="yellow">Macy’s!!</font></a> Hopefully, I can find better loot than what every Druid had on PTR, which was obviously a drop from <a href="http://wow.fohguild.org/gallery/d/1442-1/someoneisapervert.JPG"><font color="yellow">Spencers</font></a>.</font>
			
